<p><b>How do you set a quiet time?</b> Build silence into your schedule Treat quiet time like an important meeting by adding it to your calendar. Even a few minutes can make a big difference. Whether it's during your morning coffee or right before bed, find a time in your daily routine for a little bit of quiet time that works for you, and stick to it.</p>
